title: Ep. - 489 - LITTLE PEOPLE BIG WORLD AND PARIS IN LOVE WITH JULIE AND BRANDY
description:
Julie Goldman and Brandy Howard join Kate to discuss this season of Little People Big World on TLC and Paris in Love on Peacock TV.

 

Little People Big World chronicles the lives of the six-member Roloff family farm near Portland, Oregon. Paris In Love follows Paris Hilton and her fiance  Carter Reum plan their wedding. The series also stars her sister Nicky Hilton and mother Kathy Hilton.
